data.title: Events & Activities
data.meta_description: The Dallas Arboretum has something for everyone. Our world-class, seasonal festivals and exhibits, along with our luxurious private venues for weddings and corporate events.
data.text:
Hispanic Heritage Celebration

September 14 & 15

Presented by Bank of America

Join us for the 7th annual Dallas Arboretum Hispanic Heritage Celebration on September 14-15, 2024. This two day celebration will feature vendors, live music, cooking demonstrations, and the Quinceañera Fashion Show.

Learn More

Cool Thursdays Concerts Series

Presented by HilltopSecurities

Make your 2024 one to remember at the coolest spot in Dallas as we celebrate our 27th season with returning favorites and NEW acts!

Get Tickets

Tour des Fleurs

September 21

Lace up your running shoes and join us for the Tour des Fleurs on September 21! Whether you’re a seasoned runner or just looking for a fun challenge, our half & quarter marathon around White Rock Lake is perfect for you.

Register

Seated Tea

Complete your Dallas Arboretum experience with a seasonal and delicious three-course tea set amid the beautiful DeGolyer Tea Room. Reservations are required and must be made 24 hours in advance.

Learn More

Cooking Classes and Demos

Hone your skills in the kitchen with our specialized classes on how to prepare gourmet dishes.
